data.description: ****WELCOME TO YOUR DREAM COUNTRY HOME****  Talk about a beautiful lot partially cleared with gorgeous mature pine trees and what do you say about the unique  oaks entrance on both sides if the drive way forming a beautiful arch, what an statement!! The property is located only 2 miles from 99,  5 min from the heart of DAYTON and 7 min from the  NEW STARBUCKS in town.   Did I mention that the  home was recently updated with new flooring throughout the entire home, and it also has a BRAND NEW ROOF. This property also has a chicken coop, a barn and a shed. it also has a GENERAC for the entire house.
